universe of origin : the teardown — a made machine, opened and explored
seal               : Coleco's console punched straight at the arcade: a Z80, the proven TMS9918A video chip, and a pack-in port of Donkey Kong so close to the coin-op that it sold the machine on its own. An expansion module even let it play Atari 2600 games — a bold shot at the whole market.
